data.description: Beautiful 2 story home in the amazing Sweetwater community!!!   Aspire model with true 4 bedrooms + loft up, 2.5 baths, 2 car garage, full basement!    Efficient and functional, open layout with modern finishes and upgrades! Dark cabinets, granite counters, back splash, stainless steel appliances, pantry, and island make this kitchen complete for any living/entertaining situation!  Mudroom setup to accommodate any number of occupants/guests! 1st floor den/office.  Hardwood floors! 2nd floor laundry! and a full unfinished basement is ready for you to put the final touches!
